Name: {NICKNAME}
Desc: A {F#girl}{M#boy} who boarded the Astral Express.\nThey chose to travel with the Astral Express to eliminate the dangers posed by the Stellaron.

1.Name: Best Seat in the House
1.Desc: Recovers <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Skill Point(s) after using the Skill for the first time in a battle.

2.Name: Jailbreaking Rainbowwalk
2.Desc: At the start of the battle, the Trailblazer's Energy Regeneration Rate increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>, lasting for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

3.Name: Sanatorium for Rest Notes
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>. Talent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

4.Name: Dove in Tophat
4.Desc: Increases the Break Effect of all allies except the Trailblazer. The increase is equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of the Trailblazer's Break Effect plus <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.

5.Name: Poem Favors Rhythms of Old
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>. Basic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

6.Name: Tomorrow, Rest in Spotlight
6.Desc: Increases the Skill's additional DMG by <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> hit(s).

800601.Name: Swing Dance Etiquette
800601.Desc: Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of the Trailblazer's ATK to a single enemy.

800602.Name: Halftime to Make It Rain
800602.Desc: Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Trailblazer's ATK to a single enemy and deals DMG for 4 extra times, dealing Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Trailblazer's ATK to a random enemy each time.

800603.Name: All-Out Footlight Parade
800603.Desc: Applies the Backup Dancer effect to all allies, lasting for <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> turn(s). Decreases its duration by 1 turn at the start of Trailblazer's every turn. When allied targets with Backup Dancer attack an enemy in the <u>Weakness Broken state</u>, they will deal <u>Break DMG</u> 1 additional time based on <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of the attacker's Break DMG and the current attack's Toughness-Reducing DMG.

800604.Name: Full-on Aerial Dance
800604.Desc: The Trailblazer immediately regenerates <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[f1]</unbreak></color> Energy when an enemy target's Weakness is Broken.

800606.Name: Attack
800606.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

800607.Name: Now! I'm the Band!
800607.Desc: After using the Technique, at the start of the next battle, all allies' Break Effect increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>, lasting for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

1.PointDesc: When there are 5 or more enemy targets, the Break DMG triggered by the Backup Dancer effect increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. For every enemy target reduced, the Break DMG triggered by the Backup Dancer effect additionally increases by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.
Additionally increases the first Toughness-Reducing DMG inflicted by the Skill in a battle by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.
Additionally delays the enemy target's action by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> when teammates Break enemy Weaknesses.
